---
source: tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Manage terminology

Usage: mf term [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  list   List terms
  new    Create a term
  lint   Lint term consistency in project docs
  learn  Learn a term correction
  fix    Fix a term metadata

Options:
      --root <PATH>      
      --config <PATH>    
  -v, --verbose...       
  -q, --quiet            
      --format <FORMAT>  [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
      --no-color         
  -h, --help             Print help
  -V, --version          Print version
